 & \TT\exp\left(-\ii\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\left(\TT\exp\left(-\ii\int_{-\infty}^{y_{1}^{0}}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\right)^{\dagger}\\
 & \qquad=\TT\exp\left(-\ii\int_{y_{1}^{0}}^{\infty}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\underbrace{\TT\exp\left(-\ii\int_{-\infty}^{y_{1}^{0}}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\left(\TT\exp\left(-\ii\int_{-\infty}^{y_{1}^{0}}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\right)^{\dagger}}_{=\mathbbm{1}}=\\
 & \qquad=\TT\exp\left(-\ii\int_{y_{1}^{0}}^{\infty}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Man erhält also:
\begin_inset Formula 
