 & \quad=\leftidx{_{I,t_{\infty}\negthickspace\negthickspace}}{\BraKet{0|\TT\exp\left(\frac{1}{\ii}\int_{y_{1}^{0}}^{\infty}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\hat{\phi}_{I}\left(y_{1}\right)\TT\exp\left(\frac{1}{\ii}\int_{y_{2}^{0}}^{y_{1}^{0}}\dd\tau H_{I}\left(\tau\right)\right)\hat{\phi}_{I}\left(y_{2}\right)\ldots|0}}{_{\negthickspace I,t_{-\infty}}}=\\
